      <title>交易员减少对欧洲央行进一步降息的押注，欧元上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/euro-jumps-as-traders-pare-wagers-on-further-ecb-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧洲央行周四宣布降息但上调通胀预期之后，交易员减少了对该行进一步降息的押注，导致欧元上涨，债券下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/euro-jumps-as-traders-pare-wagers-on-further-ecb-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:29:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
